### ==========================================
### 1. AUTHENTICATION
### ==========================================

### Register an Admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Admin User",
  "username": "admin1",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "admin"
}

###

### Login (Copy the token from the response)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin1",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Get Current User Profile (Needs Token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ==========================================
### 2. USER MANAGEMENT (Admin Only)
### ==========================================

### Get All Users
GET {{baseUrl}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ==========================================
### 3. CLASSES
### ==========================================

### Create a new Quran Class (Admin Only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/classes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "class_name": "Beginner Quran A",
  "type": "Quran",
  "teacher_id": 1 
}

### View All Classes
GET {{baseUrl}}/classes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ==========================================
### 4. STUDENTS
### ==========================================

### Create a Student (Admin Only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/students
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Ahmed Ali",
  "contact_info": "123-456-7890",
  "parent_info": "Ali Muhammad",
  "date_of_birth": "2010-05-15"
}

### Get All Students
GET {{baseUrl}}/students
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ==========================================
### 5. ENROLLMENTS
### ==========================================

### Enroll a Student in a Class
POST {{baseUrl}}/enrollments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "student_id": 1,
  "class_id": 1
}

### Get All Enrollments
GET {{baseUrl}}/enrollments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ==========================================
### 6. SCHEDULES (Dynamic Calendar)
### ==========================================

### Setup Schedule for a Month
POST {{baseUrl}}/schedules
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "month_year": "2026-02",
  "weekend_config": [5, 6], 
  "manual_overrides": {
    "2026-02-15": "Passive",
    "2026-02-28": "Active"
  }
}

### Get Schedule and Active Day Metrics
GET {{baseUrl}}/schedules/2026-02
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ==========================================
### 7. PROGRESS & ATTENDANCE
### ==========================================

### Log Quran Progress (Automatically marks student as Present)
POST {{baseUrl}}/progress/quran
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "enrollment_id": 1,
  "date": "2026-02-10",
  "type": "Hifz",
  "surah_id": 1,
  "start_verse": 1,
  "end_verse": 7,
  "rating": 5
}

### Get Progress for a single enrollment
GET {{baseUrl}}/progress/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Mark general attendance for a day (Batch)
POST {{baseUrl}}/attendance
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date": "2026-02-12",
  "attendanceList": [
    {
      "enrollment_id": 1,
      "status": "Absent"
    }
  ]
}

### Get Attendance for a class on a specific date
GET {{baseUrl}}/attendance/1/2026-02-12
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
